headline: Why Thermo Fisher (TMO) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of life sciences company Thermo Fisher (NYSE:TMO) jumped 2.9% in the afternoon session after the company launched a new high-performance panel to accelerate neurodegenerative disease research and received a positive analyst rating.
